# AUDIO::SET_AGGRESSIVE_HORNS

## Parameters
* **BOOL** enable

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Makes pedestrians sound their horn longer, faster and more agressive when they use their horn.
